longBusinessSummary: DFV Deutsche Familienversicherung AG operates as a digital insurance company in Germany. It offers dental, health, supplementary long-term care, hospital, daily sickness allowance, international travel health, outpatient, accident, and state-aided care provision insurance; property insurance, such as personal liability, household, and dog liability insurance; dog and cat health insurance; and legal expense and electronics insurance products.  DFV Deutsche Familienversicherung AG was incorporated in 2006 and is based Frankfurt, Germany.
